      "created": "2017-10-27T00:22:55.532+0000",
      "description": "Each RM in a federation should bias its local allocations of containers based on the global over/under utilization of queues. As part of this the local RM should account for the work that other RMs will be doing in between the updates we receive via the heartbeats of YARN-7404 (the mechanics used for synchronization).",
